Package: shinyhighlightr
Title: Create Text Markup Input Controls with 'Shiny'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person('Stefanie Schneider', email = 'stefanie.schneider@itg.uni-muenchen.de', role = c('cre', 'aut'), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4915-6949"))
Maintainer: Stefanie Schneider <stefanie.schneider@itg.uni-muenchen.de>
Description: Create text markup input controls to highlight patterns in text values. Two input fields are created: one to specify the expression to be marked; another where this expression is marked in unstructured text values, e.g., test cases for a regular expression.
